data.description: Welcome to Rotunda Lofts, downtown's iconic address! Experience true urban living with exposed piping, concrete beams, granite counters, wood floors, and rich cherry cabinets. This former model unit boasts unique design features including panoramic windows with city views and industrial loft aesthetics. Enjoy a full appliance package with washer and dryer, on-site parking, and security in this pet-friendly building. Walk to all venues including the new Waterside District from this one-of-a-kind 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom urban condo on the 2nd floor. With only 8 units like this, featuring concrete floors, exposed columns, and piping, this is a rare find in the heart of downtown.
